data.description: LOOKING FOR A LARGE MASTER BEDROOM? Well You've Found It. Located in a great neighborhood convenient to shopping and all major interstates. This home has lots of features including an open foyer, loft, step down great room with fireplace, bedroom/bathroom on main level and many more. This home is great for entertaining your guest. Nice size yard with utility shed for storage. Enjoy the great amenities Hampton Place have to offer which includes: pool, tennis, & playground. Welcome Home!!!
